@startuml
[*] --> Registering : create new account
Registering --> Registered : validation successful
Registered --> LoggedIn : login submitted
LoggedIn --> TicketStatusCheck : check ticket status
LoggedIn --> BookingTicket : book a ticket
BookingTicket --> PaymentConfirmed : payment made
PaymentConfirmed --> TicketBooked : booking confirmed
LoggedIn --> ManagingAccount : manage account details
ManagingAccount --> AccountDetailsUpdated : edit or delete account
LoggedIn --> LoggedOut : logout
@enduml
